name: Reveal Ourselves To The Jedi
Lore: 'Darth Maul was eager to make his presence known.',
Text: 'Use 5 Force to reveal opponent''s hand. If opponent has no duplicate cards there, place this Interrupt in Used Pile. Otherwise USED: place a card revealed in opponent''s Used Pile,LOST: all cards opponent has two or more of are lost. (Immune to Sense.)',
